    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Créer une simple extension Wordpress]]></title>
    <link href="http://tym-project.github.com/2011/01/26/plugin-wordpress-modification-de-texte/"/>
    <updated>2011-01-26T21:07:15+00:00</updated>
